<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>직접 선택 예약</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/tailwind.min.css">
    <script src="/js/lucide.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 min-h-screen flex flex-col">
    <main class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto p-8">
        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            <div class="mb-6">
                <a href="/reservation" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-800 font-medium transition-colors">
                    <i data-lucide="arrow-left" class="w-5 h-5"></i> 뒤로 가기
                </a>
            </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 p-8">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600">
                    <i data-lucide="calendar" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">진료 예약</h1>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 mt-1">원하시는 진료과와 시간을 선택해주세요.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <form action="/reservation/submit" method="POST" class="space-y-6">
                <input type="hidden" name="symptoms" value="">

                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">환자 성함</label>
                        <div class="relative">
                            <i data-lucide="user" class="absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-5 h-5 text-slate-400"></i>
                            <input type="text" name="patientName" value="" required class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-3 border border-slate-300 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 outline-none" placeholder="홍길동"/>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">연락처</label>
                        <div class="relative">
                            <i data-lucide="phone" class="absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-5 h-5 text-slate-400"></i>
                            <input type="tel" name="phone" value="" required class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-3 border border-slate-300 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 outline-none" placeholder="010-1234-5678"/>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">진료과</label>
                        <select name="departmentId" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-slate-300 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 outline-none bg-white">
                            <option value="">선택해주세요</option>
                            <option value="1">내과</option>
                            <option value="2">이비인후과</option>
                            <option value="3">정형외과</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">전문의</label>
                        <select name="doctorId" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-slate-300 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 outline-none bg-white">
                            <option value="">선택해주세요</option>
                            <option value="1">김원장</option>
                            <option value="2">이원장</option>
                            <option value="3">박원장</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">예약 날짜</label>
                        <div class="relative">
                            <i data-lucide="calendar" class="absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-5 h-5 text-slate-400"></i>
                            <input type="date" name="reservationDate" required class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-3 border border-slate-300 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 outline-none"/>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">예약 시간</label>
                        <div class="relative">
                            <i data-lucide="clock" class="absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-5 h-5 text-slate-400"></i>
                            <select name="reservationTime" required class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-3 border border-slate-300 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 outline-none bg-white">
                                <option value="">선택해주세요</option>
                                <option value="09:00">09:00</option>
                                <option value="09:30">09:30</option>
                                <option value="10:00">10:00</option>
                                <option value="10:30">10:30</option>
                                <option value="11:00">11:00</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="pt-6 border-t border-slate-200">
                    <button type="submit" class="w-full py-4 bg-indigo-600 text-white rounded-xl font-medium text-lg hover:bg-indigo-700 transition-colors shadow-sm">
                        예약 완료하기
                    </button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </main>

    <script>
        lucide.createIcons();
    </script>
</body>
</html>
